#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.29:4.1"
msgid "1.29. Hāritattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.29. Hārita (1st)"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns29"></a><a class="vnp"
#. id="vnp29"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.29:5.1"
msgid "“Samunnamayamattānaṃ,"
msgstr "Straighten yourself,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.29:5.2"
msgid "usukārova tejanaṃ;"
msgstr "like a fletcher straightens an arrow."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.29:5.3"
msgid "Cittaṃ ujuṃ karitvāna,"
msgstr "When your mind is upright, Hārita,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.29:5.4"
msgid "avijjaṃ bhinda hāritā”ti."
msgstr "break ignorance to bits!"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
